              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Auditions</span>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-4 coustard-regular">Custom Audition Forms</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">Build audition forms with the questions you need. Upload cuts, set deadlines, and collect video submissions—all in one place.</p>
              <ul class="text-slate-600 space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-pink-500 mt-1">✓</span>
                  <span>Upload audio cuts and sheet music</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-pink-500 mt-1">✓</span>
                  <span>Collect video submissions with deadlines</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-pink-500 mt-1">✓</span>
                  <span>Ask any questions you need answered</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-2/3">
